<h1>High Match Alert!</h1>
<p>Hi {{ownerName}},</p>
<p>Great news! A tenant with a highly compatible profile is interested in your room: <strong>{{roomTitle}}</strong>.</p>

<div class="highlight-box">
  <p style="margin-top: 0; font-weight: 600;">Tenant Details:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{tenantName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Compatibility Score:</strong> {{compatibilityScore}}%</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>Log in to review their profile and accept their request if you'd like to chat!</p>

<a href="{{platformUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}" class="btn">View Request</a>
